  "rationale": "<p>Perform polynomial division: x<sup>2</sup> &minus; 4x &minus; 7 = (x &minus; 5)(x + 1) + (&minus;2). Therefore the expression equals (x + 1) + (&minus;2)/(x &minus; 5) = x + 1 &minus; 2/(x &minus; 5). The other options correspond to common errors (wrong quotient or wrong remainder).</p>",
